    <item>
      <title>丰田在日本和中国销量下降，而混合动力车在美国销量增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/toyota-sales-fall-in-japan-china-as-hybrids-make-gains-in-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管北美对混合动力汽车的需求强劲，但丰田汽车公司在日本和中国的销售仍面临一系列挑战，包括来自电动汽车品牌的竞争加剧、国内丑闻以及海外召回事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/toyota-sales-fall-in-japan-china-as-hybrids-make-gains-in-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 04:30:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国 45 亿美元基金正在购买股票，关注衍生品</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/thailand-s-4-5-billion-fund-is-buying-stocks-eyes-derivatives</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位联合投资经理透露，泰国新成立的 45 亿美元国有投资基金已经开始购买股票，并正在考虑使用股票衍生品来保护其资本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/thailand-s-4-5-billion-fund-is-buying-stocks-eyes-derivatives</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 04:17:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国遏制中国科技发展的努力为何举步维艰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-30/why-us-efforts-to-contain-china-tech-push-are-faltering-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管历届美国政府都对中国实施关税、出口管制和金融制裁，但中国在主导未来行业方面仍取得了稳步进展。彭博情报和彭博经济的最新研究表明，北京的产业政策蓝图“中国制造 2025”在很大程度上取得了成功。彭博情报高级分析师罗伯特·李和亚洲政府与经济通讯员丽贝卡·钟·威尔金斯在“彭博：中国秀”中讨论了这些发现。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-30/why-us-efforts-to-contain-china-tech-push-are-faltering-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 03:56:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>康瑞增强为超强台风，即将袭击台湾</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/kong-rey-strengthens-into-super-typhoon-on-track-for-taiwan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[康蕾已增强为超强台风，它绕过菲律宾向台湾前进，预计周四在台湾附近地区登陆，该地区几周前曾遭受过强烈台风袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/kong-rey-strengthens-into-super-typhoon-on-track-for-taiwan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 03:33:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>道富银行称黄金可能还有进一步上涨空间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-30/gold-may-have-further-upside-state-street-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[道富环球投资管理公司首席黄金策略师乔治·米林-斯坦利 (George Milling-Stanley) 讨论了贵金属的涨势及其前景。周三亚洲早盘，金价创下历史新高。米林-斯坦利在“彭博：中国秀”上发表讲话，称黄金是“终极避险资产”。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-30/gold-may-have-further-upside-state-street-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 03:27:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>渣打银行警告称，受中东风险影响，美国大选后油价可能飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/oil-may-spike-after-us-election-on-mideast-risk-stanchart-warns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[渣打银行表示，石油市场对中东风险的“放松过快”，而美国大选后以色列和伊朗之间重新爆发的敌对情绪可能会推高油价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/oil-may-spike-after-us-election-on-mideast-risk-stanchart-warns</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 03:22:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
